riak from basho
(5 minute installation)

1a) install dependencies and  erlang
1b) install 1 node on local and start the node

2a) build riak and start 5 nodes, pre-install Rebar 
2b) join and leave cluster
2c) multisite

3) python client
4) put/fetch props
5) put/fetch an image

1-2) installation
http://docs.basho.com/riak/latest/quickstart/#Start-Up-Five-Nodes

3) client
http://docs.basho.com/riak/latest/dev/taste-of-riak/python/


